c66x Directory Reference

Files

file  dsp_config.h
 This file contains the API prototypes for DSP configuration.
 
file  dsp_ecc.h
 ECC API declarations for DSP Internal memory (L1P and L2) ECC.
 
file  dsp_icfg.h
 This file contains the prototypes of the APIs present in the device abstraction layer file of ICFG in the C66x DSP subsytems. This also include related macro definitions. All APIs should be called with interrupts disabled to ensure coherency.
 
file  dsp_usrSpvSupport.h
 This file contains the API prototypes for configuring mode of DSP (User/Supervisor)
 
file  dsp_wugen.h
 This file contains the API prototypes for configuring DSP_WUGEN for DSP.
 
file  dsp_xmc.h
 This file contains the implementation of the APIs present in the device abstraction layer file of Extended Memory Controller (XMC) in the C66x DSP subsytems. This also include related macro definitions. All APIs should be called with interrupts disabled to ensure coherency.
 
file  hw_dsp_icfg.h
 register-level header file for DSP
 
file  hw_dsp_system.h
 register-level header file for DSP
 
file  hw_xmc.h
 
file  c66x/interrupt.h
 This file contains the API prototypes for configuring INTC for DSP.
